videos.description: Tyler Cook tracks down the missed layup and goes up to slam it home as it comes off the rim.
videos.headline: Iowa's Cook cleans up miss with strong dunk

videos.description: Iowa's Cordell Pemsl comes racing in to Connor McCaffery's defense after he and Iowa State's Michael Jacobson get tangled up and exchange choice words.
videos.headline: Tempers flare in 1st half between Iowa and Iowa State

videos.description: Marial Shayok drives to the rack and puts up a wild layup that somehow bounces in off the top of the backboard.
videos.headline: Shayok makes difficult layup off the top of the backboard

videos.description: Marial Shayok drives hard to the rack and makes the defender think twice about contesting him as he rises up and smashes down a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Shayok crushes a monster dunk
